m/news/art/20140813/18830558</a><br />\n2014年，做乜鳩呀 又回帶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46eeeb46950781b57c31288cfbc8c31499aca95","tid":280620,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:15:49.000Z","msg":"洗女最愛有錢佬 完"},{"pid":"cab7d76422acaa406aac53a149dc6824ae01e8d4","tid":280620,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"阿媽係女人<br />\n山係石頭海係水"},{"pid":"77c9508428f5a3df8cac7f9de1606d839634fdbe","tid":280620,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:32:58.000Z","msg":"其實做會計真係好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e14dd8c156dbbdeb571e1a338aab2a456321ae5","tid":280620,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>「女士年紀越大，越緊張男士做乜嘢職業」。紅線婚姻顧問李威廉指，28歲以上女性以職業和收入作考慮因素，一般公務員包括消防等紀律部隊最「吃香」。有緣人負責人Maggie指揀選公務員亦要分階級：「要睇係合約定係長俸制，因為福利、人工都唔同。」<br />\n<br />\n輪唔輪到佢地梗啊</blockquote><br />\n28歲以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n28歲以上仲想揀<br />\n笑撚死人咩 月經都就黎停仲想揀<br />\n到時m巾都無撚得揀啦屌<br />\n慳d啦 比人屌到閪又黑又鬆 仲想揀ibanker<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n越窮越見鬼</blockquote><br />\n想姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵到駛上去相體咩</blockquote><br />\n上面成班傻仔中哂蘋果計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就係想你地發哂茅<br />\n男人夠想搵個36 24 36又聽教聽話既女友<br />\n想下有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你見到有報導報男人想要呢種女友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\non9</blockquote><br />\n你覺得唔係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係唔明有乜好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你問人理想類型，就梗係條條女答你想要王子<br />\n同樣道理，男人都會想要波長腿一樣<br />\n但想就梗係同現實兩回事"},{"pid":"a7eac8f7841e22a6861a577f2e72027553e04822","tid":280620,"uid":103346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>調查發現 港女最愛<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">錢</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實全世界D女都係, 但港女特別蠢.</blockquote><br />\n我都想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2fada975ed317d742f2d821ebd922066e15e1f5","tid":280620,"uid":99530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單身男女揀對象，除了外貌、性格、談吐舉止外，職業都是重要指標。《蘋果》訪問了全港10間較具規模的婚介及速配公司，綜合他們的調查發現，女性最愛投資銀行家（iBanker），而任職護士和老師的女性，則在男士首選之列。「女士年紀越大，越緊張男士做乜嘢職業」。紅線婚姻顧問李威廉指，28歲以上女性以職業和收入作考慮因素，一般公務員包括消防等紀律部隊最「吃香」。有緣人負責人Maggie指揀選公務員亦要分階級：「要睇係合約定係長俸制，因為福利、人工都唔同。」而男性較緊張女性年紀和外貌，Speed Dating Fever負責人黃新發說，大部份男性不會選擇薪酬高於自己的女性：「男仔多數要求睇相，同埋希望對方細自己三至五年。」至於最抗拒的職業，男女卻很一致，普遍對零售和保險等銷售工作最反感，「開始認識時會避忌，擔心有推銷目的，或者為人會較勢利」。<span style=\"color: red;\">香港性教育會會長黎定基</span>表示，從職業分析男女擇偶條件，明顯看到女性要求對方有經濟能力及事業心，既存在「嫁個有錢郎」的心態，又怕對方花心，故希望對方是一名專業人士多於是一名富商，反而男性只望伴侶有穩定職業，更易於駕馭對方。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真實存在?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd957bffc3435f9b54daef9a7011f5e460cfebe6","tid":280620,"uid":3002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"調查發現港女最愛錢"},{"pid":"cc5d4c6375f0054ed6fddf2d77da0c1478c4484d","tid":280620,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:52:20.000Z","msg":"話iBankers and lawyers悶既 九成都唔識幾個 係度幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af470f6ee438e0276029ac9ffb4b26e740574234","tid":280620,"uid":22387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T11:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人睇錢，收入，呢d隨年紀會越揾越多<br />\n男人睇樣，身材，呢d隨年紀會走下坡<br />\n<br />\n結論:男人等得，女人好急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到悶<br />\n現實係女人未到死唔知錯"},{"pid":"9bc578c3321afec4c8d14d29268c006dc77bb28d","tid":280620,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T11:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係做得呢d工既男人一定份人好悶<br />\n一係咁有錢一定會出軌<br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地要結婚，要有個可以拎出去同d姐妹曬既老公</blockquote><br />\n律師其實可以好花心呀"},{"pid":"41cbeca62d20f92a391537bb445a2e8cb57323b7","tid":280620,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T11:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話iBankers and lawyers悶既 九成都唔識幾個 係度幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做得呢d職業社交能力差極有限<br />\n<br />\n班人講到自己幾風趣幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現實就係死毒撚粒聲唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}